  "84393911-8a58-466b-98fe-24ae5ed79de7:67": [
    {
      "op": "update",
      "notebookId": "notebook-1779809073231_xe7d25oua",
      "previousNote": "2026-05-26 update 7: Latest NativeFileMount paste fixes. Frontend paste now sends conflictStrategy=ask first and only opens an in-widget conflict dialog when backend returns ERR_CONFLICT_NEEDS_CONFIRM; dialog options are 覆盖 (overwrite+confirmed), 重命名 (autoRename), 取消. pasteToCurrentDir uses currentDir || rootPath so mount-root paste does not send an empty destDir. Backend _paste now pre-resolves all conflicts before creating the async copy job, so conflict errors are returned synchronously to the widget instead of being hidden in job failure; affectedPaths includes destination paths. Windows Explorer interop changed from Electron FileNameW-only to PowerShell file clipboard support: _writeSystemFileClipboard uses Set-Clipboard -LiteralPath and _readSystemFileClipboard uses Get-Clipboard -Format FileDropList, with Electron FileNameW as fallback. Backend tracks a clipboard signature so Explorer-copied files can override stale internal globalClipboard. node --check passed for nativeFileMountWidget.js and NativeFsService.js."
    }
  ],
  "998a3d13-db5a-43b2-863a-a2f3d415465b:54": [
    {
      "op": "add",
      "notebookId": "notebook-1779813688928_1g6lmvy4q"
    }
  ],
  "f84d5558-a97d-4d56-8bd2-3b6018a69018:61": [
    {
      "op": "update",
      "notebookId": "notebook-1779813688928_1g6lmvy4q",
      "previousNote": "2026-05-27 NativeFileMount follow-up: implemented accepted paste conflict optimization and UX changes. Backend NativeFsService now supports clipboardPreview as a readonly action, caches internal clipboard preview after copy/cut, builds preview from the currently effective internal/system clipboard, and _paste() fast-fails on the first ask-conflict before job creation. Frontend now calls clipboardPreview quietly, predicts same-name conflicts from currently loaded entries and prompts immediately when possible, then still lets backend ask-conflict validation be authoritative. Toolbar paste button moved next to cut; row context menu now includes “粘贴到当前文件夹” and it always pastes to currentDir/rootPath, not into the selected row. NativeFsJobs now enriches failed job errors with operation/src/dest details and uses message before code; Windows EPERM during move/cut now falls back to copy+trash like EXDEV. Syntax checks passed for NativeFsJobs.js, NativeFsService.js, and nativeFileMountWidget.js."
    }
  ],
  "4107fe56-561a-4d48-885c-9317928324af:16": [
    {
      "op": "update",
      "notebookId": "notebook-1779813688928_1g6lmvy4q",
      "previousNote": "2026-05-27 NativeFileMount follow-up: implemented accepted paste conflict optimization and UX changes. Backend NativeFsService supports clipboardPreview as a readonly action, caches internal clipboard preview after copy/cut, builds preview from the currently effective internal/system clipboard, and _paste() fast-fails on the first ask-conflict before job creation. Frontend calls clipboardPreview quietly, predicts same-name conflicts from currently loaded entries and prompts immediately when possible, then still lets backend ask-conflict validation be authoritative. Toolbar paste button moved next to cut; row context menu includes “粘贴到当前文件夹” and it always pastes to currentDir/rootPath, not into the selected row. NativeFsJobs enriches failed job errors with operation/src/dest details and uses message before code; Windows EPERM during move/cut falls back to copy+trash like EXDEV. 2026-05-27 fix: same-folder copy+paste of the same file with conflict choice “重命名” previously failed because _paste() compared source with the initial requestedDest before _resolveConflict(); the guard now runs after _resolveConflict() and compares source with the final resolved dest, so autoRename can create “name (1).ext” while overwrite/self-final-dest is still rejected. Syntax checks passed for NativeFsJobs.js, NativeFsService.js, and nativeFileMountWidget.js."
    }
  ],
